  "title": "Refuse Truck Driver",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong><br />• Driving a Rear End Loader (REL) truck to perform Refuse collection in accordance with the schedule<br />• Operation of the REL truck to empty bins and transfer bins to the hopper.<br />• Assist attendant during recycling waste collection<br />• Washing the truck and cleaning the interior.<br />• Performing and recording minor maintenance tasks<br />• Labouring work as required to complete recycling collection jobs.</p><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong><br />• Hold a Class 4/ 5 driving licence is a must.<br />• Have a minimum of 2 years of heavy-moving truck and manual or semi auto transmission REL driving experience<br />• Prefer to have WSQ (PI-WM-106E-1) certificate.<br />• Prefer to have own transport and stay at West Area</p><p>• Singaporean / PR Only</p>",
